{"id": "art-2521", "label": "Art. 2521", "title": "Art. 2521: Cazuri speciale de valorificare a bunurilor mobile şi imobile sechestrate", "slug": "art-2521", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 252<sup>1</sup>: Cazuri speciale de valorificare a bunurilor mobile\n&#351;i imobile sechestrate </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1933109317\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2084\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1933109317\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)În cursul procesului penal, înainte de pronun&#355;area\nunei hot&#259;râri definitive, procurorul, judec&#259;torul de camer&#259;\npreliminar&#259; sau, dup&#259; caz, instan&#355;a de judecat&#259; care a\ninstituit sechestrul poate dispune de îndat&#259; valorificarea bunurilor\nmobile sau imobile sechestrate, la cererea proprietarului bunurilor sau atunci\ncând exist&#259; acordul acestuia.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_659060749\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2083\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_659060749\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cursul\nprocesului penal, înainte de pronun&#355;area unei hot&#259;râri definitive,\natunci când nu exist&#259; acordul proprietarului, bunurile mobile asupra\nc&#259;rora s-a instituit sechestrul asigur&#259;tor pot fi valorificate, în\nmod excep&#355;ional, în urm&#259;toarele situa&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1062122569\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2082\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1062122569\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)atunci când, în termen de un an de la data instituirii\nsechestrului, valoarea bunurilor sechestrate s-a diminuat în mod semnificativ,\nrespectiv cu cel pu&#355;in 40% în raport cu cea de la momentul dispunerii\nm&#259;surii asigur&#259;torii. Dispozi&#355;iile art. 252 alin. (1) se\naplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor &#351;i în acest caz;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2111803685\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2081\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2111803685\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)atunci când exist&#259; riscul expir&#259;rii termenului\nde garan&#355;ie sau când sechestrul asigur&#259;tor s-a aplicat asupra unor\nanimale sau p&#259;s&#259;ri vii;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1353305442\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2080\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1353305442\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)atunci când sechestrul asigur&#259;tor s-a aplicat asupra\nproduselor inflamabile sau petroliere, asupra masei lemnoase &#351;i a\nmaterialelor lemnoase, asupra produselor farmaceutice &#351;i a materialelor\nsanitare;</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_231906981\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2079\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_231906981\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)atunci când sechestrul asigur&#259;tor s-a aplicat asupra\nunor bunuri a c&#259;ror depozitare sau între&#355;inere necesit&#259;\ncheltuieli dispropor&#355;ionate în raport cu valoarea bunului.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_85789008\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2078\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_85789008\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)atunci când sechestrul asigur&#259;tor s-a aplicat asupra\nunui stoc de bunuri sau produse cu o valoare cumulat&#259; mai mic&#259; sau\negal&#259; cu echivalentul în lei al sumei de 300.000 euro.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_744942736\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2077\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_744942736\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În cursul\nprocesului penal, înainte de pronun&#355;area unei hot&#259;râri definitive,\natunci când sunt îndeplinite cumulativ urm&#259;toarele condi&#355;ii:\nproprietarul nu a putut fi identificat &#351;i valorificarea nu se poate face\npotrivit alin. (2), autovehiculele asupra c&#259;rora s-a instituit sechestrul\nasigur&#259;tor pot fi valorificate, în urm&#259;toarele situa&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_767518436\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2076\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_767518436\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)atunci când acestea au fost folosite, în orice mod, la\ns&#259;vâr&#351;irea unei infrac&#355;iuni;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_553245086\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2075\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_553245086\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)dac&#259; de la data instituirii m&#259;surii\nasigur&#259;torii asupra acestor bunuri a trecut o perioad&#259; de un an sau\nmai mare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_498169049\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2074\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_498169049\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3<sup>1</sup>)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>În\ncursul procesului penal, înainte de pronun&#355;area unei hot&#259;râri\ndefinitive, atunci când sechestrul asigur&#259;tor s-a aplicat asupra unui\nmijloc de transport rutier, feroviar, naval sau aerian &#351;i valorificarea nu\nse poate face potrivit dispozi&#355;iilor alin. (2), bunurile pot fi\nvalorificate, atunci când sunt îndeplinite cumulativ urm&#259;toarele\ncondi&#355;ii:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1913259030\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2073\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1913259030\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)m&#259;sura asigur&#259;torie a fost dispus&#259; pentru\na evita ascunderea, distrugerea, înstr&#259;inarea sau sustragerea de la\nurm&#259;rire a bunurilor care pot face obiectul confisc&#259;rii speciale sau\nal confisc&#259;rii extinse;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_755585953\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2072\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_755585953\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în termen de un an de la data instituirii m&#259;surii\nasigur&#259;torii proprietarul nu consemneaz&#259;, în contul constituit\npotrivit legii speciale, o sum&#259; de bani în cuantum egal cu valoarea\nbunului sechestrat;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1374932498\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2071\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1374932498\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)bunul se afl&#259; în custodia unei institu&#355;ii\npublice.</span><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1861613048\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2070\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1861613048\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Sumele de bani rezultate din valorificarea bunurilor\nmobile f&#259;cut&#259; potrivit alin. (1)-(3<sup>1</sup>) se depun în contul\nprev&#259;zut la art. 252 alin. (8).</span><br style='mso-special-character:\nline-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1929632703\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2069\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1929632703\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)[textul din Art. 252^1, alin. (5) din partea 1, titlul\nV, capitolul III a fost abrogat la 27-dec-2015 de </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Art. 47, punctul 2. din capitolul VIII din Legea 318/2015</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>]</span></p>"}